# CODEOWNERS — defines who must review changes to sensitive paths.
#
# GitHub requires these reviewers to approve before merge can proceed
# (when "require code owner review" is enabled in branch protection).
# Reviews are requested automatically when a PR touches a listed path.
#
# Format: <pattern> <@user or @org/team>

